  <brief_title>Colchicine in ST-elevation Myocardial Infarction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Anti-inflammatory Treatment With Colchicine in the Acute Phase of ST-elevation Myocardial Infarction to Reduce Infarct Size</official_title>
